PrecisApproval of Regulations Amending the CANADA GRAIN REGULATIONS which make assorted minor amendments or corrections designed to make the Regulations easier to comprehend and to consult, provide for the making of solemn affirmations as an alternative to taking an oath of office, and reflect current procedures and practices of the Commission as well as changes in grain-movement patterns.

precis:
Approval of Regulations Amending the CANADA GRAIN REGULATIONS which make
assorted minor amendments or corrections designed to make the Regulations
easier to comprehend and to consult, provide for the making of solemn
affirmations as an alternative to taking an oath of office, and reflect
current procedures and practices of the Commission as well as changes in
grain-movement patterns.
